ets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/08/ff22405c3e405540366f1940198cef5c-kix.1zytezz7j3xu-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/08/ff22405c3e405540366f1940198cef5c-kix.1zytezz7j3xu-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/08/ff22405c3e405540366f1940198cef5c-kix.1zytezz7j3xu-300x188.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/08/ff22405c3e405540366f1940198cef5c-kix.1zytezz7j3xu-768x480.webp 768w" width="1000" height="625" /></a><br /> （摘自 <a href="https://x.com/kamitsubaki_tcg/status/1821514143121440933" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《神椿卡牌游戏官方X</a> 》）</p><p>集换式卡牌游戏<strong>“KAMITSUBAKI CARD GAME”</strong>已发布。我们将于8月21日（周三）开始在FINDME STORE by THINKR接受订单，信息将逐步在<a href="https://x.com/kamitsubaki_tcg" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Official X（原Twitter）</a>上发布。此外，KAMITSUBAKI STUDIO官方Discord上还开通了卡牌游戏频道。</p><p> © 神椿工作室/SINKA 动画项目<br />（参考）<a href="https://x.com/kamitsubaki_jp" target="_blank" rel="noopener">神椿工作室官方X（旧Twitter）</a> ，<a href="https://kamitsubaki-anime.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">动画官方网站</a></p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/kamitsubaki-studio-2024-project/">KAMITSUBAKI STUDIO 发布了电视动画《Kamitsubaki City Construction》的详细信息。宣布新厂牌《Girls Revolutionary Plan》的 6 名歌手</a>在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上首次亮相。</p> ; 
