b9222f5a942-kix.hzltbgcpom9r-768x940.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/08/641139fd86c01c72545aab9222f5a942-kix.hzltbgcpom9r-jpg.webp 1103w" width="837" height="1024" /></a></p><p> “强力职业棒球”系列竞赛项目“二十三寺甲子园2024”与体育杂志《Sports Graphic Number》的合作将于2023年8月3日（星期四）发行的第1078期之后进行。</p><p> “二十三寺甲子园”是选手们在强力职业棒球系列的“永观九人”模式下进行训练，并以联盟形式进行比赛的锦标赛。该活动由虹<a href="https://twitter.com/nijisanji_app" target="_blank" rel="noopener">山寺</a>的<a href="https://twitter.com/tenkaitukasa" target="_blank" rel="noopener">天海司</a>和<a href="https://twitter.com/maimoto_k" target="_blank" rel="noopener">麦本圭介</a>主办，近年来与KONAMI官方合作举办。</p><p>此次合作，封底将由参加“二十三寺甲子园2024”的八位管理者和两位主办方绘制的原创插图进行装饰，并将进行9页的“二十三寺甲子园2024”特辑。除了舞本圭介和天海司的开场对话外，还将对连续第二年参赛的<a href="https://twitter.com/1garashi_rika" target="_blank" rel="noopener">五十岚莉香</a>进行专访、八所参赛学校的选手名单以及一篇文章揭开“PowerPro”的魅力所在。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000486.000043732.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">文艺春树株式会社新闻稿</a></p><h2>青桐高中春雨丽奈“Puyo Puyo eSports”官方大使</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/08/641139fd86c01c72545aab9222f5a942-kix.geimqtyorrr4-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/08/641139fd86c01c72545aab9222f5a942-kix.geimqtyorrr4-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/08/641139fd86c01c72545aab9222f5a942-kix.geimqtyorrr4-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/08/641139fd86c01c72545aab9222f5a942-kix.geimqtyorrr4-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/08/641139fd86c01c72545aab9222f5a942-kix.geimqtyorrr4-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/08/641139fd86c01c72545aab9222f5a942-kix.geimqtyorrr4-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/08/641139fd86c01c72545aab9222f5a942-kix.geimqtyorrr4-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p> VTuber团体“<a href="https://www.aogirihighschool.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">青雾高中</a>”的<a href="https://x.com/harusame_urame" target="_blank" rel="noopener">春雨丽</a>被任命为“Puyo Puyo eSports”的官方大使。</p><p>今后，双方将以“全国县电子竞技2024 SAGA Puyo Puyo分区”为中心，合作活跃“Puyo Puyo”锦标赛。还计划在现场直播和锦标赛新颖方面进行合作。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="【#重要公告】今天好像有一个非常重要的公告！ [#春雨丽城#青桐高中]" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3a043Rfl4VQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000005900.000005397.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">世嘉株式会社新闻稿</a></p><h2>涩谷春红牛特别合作活动即将举办</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/08/641139fd86c01c72545aab9222f5a942-kix.sxalutqklbx-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/08/641139fd86c01c72545aab9222f5a942-kix.sxalutqklbx-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 339px) 100vw, 339px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/08/641139fd86c01c72545aab9222f5a942-kix.sxalutqklbx-jpg.webp 339w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/08/641139fd86c01c72545aab9222f5a942-kix.sxalutqklbx-212x300.webp 212w" width="339" height="480" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://twitter.com/shibuyahal" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Haru Shibuya</a>和 Red Bull 的特别合作活动<span style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255);">将于 8 月 11 日（星期日）在埼玉、千叶和东京的 34 家罗森商店（不包括“Natural Lawson”和“Lawson Store 100”）举行。</span></p><p><span style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255);">为了纪念这次合作，我们将推出限量版红牛 3 罐套装。标准版附有模切贴纸，国际天空城站前店特别版附有A6贴纸。</span></p><p><span style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255);">贴纸背面附有二维码，可让您欣赏 Haru Shibuya 在工作时收听的推荐动漫歌曲播放列表。</span></p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000143.000049143.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Red Bull Japan Co., Ltd.新闻稿</a></p><h2>将